drawn from different demon&s;trated <HI>Truths,</HI>
give a <HI>&s;en&s;ible Plea&s;ure,</HI> and a &s;tronger <HI>Conviction,</HI> to an
hone&s;t Heart, and a Lover of Truth; and I could
not but be delighted with the <HI>Univer&s;ality, Simplicity,</HI>
