and generou&s;ly hopeing and believing, that
infinit Wi&s;dom and Goodne&s;s has, or will &s;upply the
<HI>re&s;t,</HI> in his own Time and Manner, <HI>we cannot fail.</HI></P>
<P>Were I to <HI>choo&s;e</HI> for my&s;elf, con&s;idering the many
