<P>I. A Con&s;tant Endeavour after the <HI>lighte&s;t</HI> and
the <HI>lea&s;t</HI> of Meat and Drink a Man can be
tolerably ea&s;y under, is the <HI>&s;horte&s;t</HI> and mo&s;t infallible
