great <HI>Vi&s;cera,</HI> and univer&s;al <HI>Cachexies.</HI></P>
<P>The <HI>Tender</HI> therefore, and <HI>Valetudinary,</HI> ought cau|tiou&s;ly
to avoid all Occa&s;ions of <HI>catching Cold;</HI> and if
