<DIV2>
<HEAD>III. The Natural Method of Curing the Di&s;ea&s;es
of the Body, and the Di&s;orders of the Mind
depending on the Body. In Three Parts.</HEAD>
<P>IN my <HI>E&s;&s;ay</HI> on <HI>Regimen,</HI> I promi&s;ed the World
my Thoughts concerning, <HI>The natural Method of
cureing the Di&s;ea&s;es of the Body, and the Di&s;orders of
